<L>__{interior santa maria della pieta, bridge of sighs. day.}
<A>__{a young boy sings the soprano part of vivaldi's stabat mater. a piercingly pure sound in vivaldi's own church. the orchestra rehearsing is conducted by peter from the organ. ripley slips in at the back of the church. he stands and listens. peter sees him, smiles. ripley smiles back.}
<L>__{exterior venice, s.lucia railway station. day.}
